    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start. It's definitely more personal than the standard boilerplate we usually use. Can you finish the last paragraph and maybe add a sentence about how we'll keep their resume on file for future openings? I want to make sure they feel like they're part of our talent community rather than just being shut out.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Absolutely, let's wrap this up with a touch of that Austin charm and a nod to the future.\n\n---\n\nPlease know that we see great potential in you and would love to keep the door open for future opportunities. We will be keeping your resume on file and will reach out if we have any openings that match your skills and experience. In the meantime, we wish you the best of luck in your continued career journey.\n\nThank you once again for considering [Company Name] as a potential employer. We hope to stay in touch and wish you all the best in your future endeavors.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Company Name]  \n\n---\n\nI hope this helps you convey the right message while keeping the spirit of Austin alive and well. Best of luck with your next adventure, and may the best candidate win!",
